Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:12.61,OST,,0,0,0,,Mohaya imi wo nasanai na\NKuzureta machi ga niyatsuku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:18.19,OST,,0,0,0,,Tashika na mono nante nai\NWakaru hazu ga nai no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:23.03,OST,,0,0,0,,Sore demo tashikametai no dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:29.07,OST,,0,0,0,,Misetakunai mono bakari wo\NMisenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:34.65,OST,,0,0,0,,Daiji na mono sae mo mitsukaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.65,0:23:39.68,OST,,0,0,0,,Kirei na mama deiru koto wa dekinai janai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:46.51,OST,,0,0,0,,Bokura wa\NBokura wa susumou
